Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:06.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's something fascinating about stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:08.34,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}be they criminals or actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:10.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A robbery that happened before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The cornered culprit crosses through space and time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:16.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell Doc his cell phone saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she didn't figure out your true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran doesn't think I'm Shin'ichi Kudo anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the whole idea that a drug turned me into a little kid is so unbelievable,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised she almost figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to thank me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who sent all those childish text messages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make it look like Agasa's phone was really yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, she doesn't suspect you anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this morning was just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're so smart, Conan{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:43.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here! A big helping for the future sleuth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, listen! It's Shin'ichi's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:53.00,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shin'ichi Kudo here! Please leave a message after the beep...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You gave her your cell number?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay! I set it on voice mail whenever I'm with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All well and good, but don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she finds out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believe me, I'm not about to get Ran involved with the men in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's strong, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lot stronger than you think she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:19.95,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:20.99,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean her karate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! That guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Detective Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like he can't decide whether to go into that store!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's definitely suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's gonna rob the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's far more likely he's just going to buy a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be for anyone. His mom, a sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when a man goes into a jewelry store with a face that red,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's gotta be for a woman he's trying to impress, or a girlfriend he wants to please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}80,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It sure is expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:30.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And I still haven't finished paying for that ring I lost at the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:36.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I caught Miwako staring at this brooch like it was Japan's most wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you want to wow her, this is the one to buy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:41.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But remember, don't tell her I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:46.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If she thinks it's a coincidence, it'll deepen your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to take a closer look?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's for one of your children, we can adjust the size.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Go for this necklace with all the diamonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a bit too glitzy for Detective Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How long have you kids been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, Detective Sato's birthday is in April...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So her birthstone's diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's perfect! Buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't say I was getting anything for Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I take a look at that brooch, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like the design!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Sato's so lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A jewel robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NHurry! Your tranquilizer gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tranquilizer dart won't go through that helmet or that heavy coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I can't tell if the gun is real or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't use my Power Kick Shoes{cf #5} in this situation either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This neighborhood is swarming with plain-clothes detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're smart, you'll drop your gun and turn yourself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He laughed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where's all the detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm off-duty myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's going into that alley...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fire escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay right here, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,drop your gun, and calmly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something fall?{previously "Did something happen?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what was that loud noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Somebody go up and check!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Police...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this your truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened? I heard something fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-A-A dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, er, please don't move the truck or its contents
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until the ambulance and police arrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its contents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't disturb the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to finish moving this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll wait until the ambulance arrives, but after that I've gotta get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me talk to the person who hired you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nekota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? He's probably in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, call him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all this fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nekota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody's here for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've barely moved anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems a guy fell on our truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we have to put this delivery on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, hurry up and do whatever you cops have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got a schedule to keep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's our fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we hadn't cornered him on that rooftop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have jumped off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were just five kids and one unarmed man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the robber thought he was cornered,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he could've turned back and broken his way through at gunpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think he was planning to commit suicide from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or else he thought he'd survive that fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something about this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,makes me suspect it's not an ordinary robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or an ordinary suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just {\i1}happened{\i0} to bump into a jewelry store robbery in progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and when you went after the guy, he jumped off a building?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He vaulted over the barrier around the rooftop,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and fell on top of this truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An overzealous police officer kills a suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it. The media will eat us for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wasn't over-jelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was just chasing the robber like he was supposed to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we got to the roof, the robber went crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It all happened so fast, we couldn't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He jumped off the roof with no hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost as if he'd planned it from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you kids in the jewelry store when the robber attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh! We saw Detective Takagi go into the store and we followed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a jewelry store on your off hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, may I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, er, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never knew you were into jewelry, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It was for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get what you went in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The robber stole it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He surprised Ayumi and she dropped it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He put it in the pocket of his coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it should still be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a weird thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you showed up, I climbed up and checked the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't find that brooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A brooch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A present for your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:43.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It was for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure he threw it away or dropped it while running.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it fell out of his pocket when he jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, you can forget about that brooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if we find it, it'll have to be kept as evidence for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who'd want a piece of jewelry with such a gruesome past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's nothing wrong with the brooch itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can just wipe off the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's other weird stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The robber was wearing a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after the fall, his head was smashed open,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like he'd taken the helmet off in mid-air!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And back at the store, when you said you were a cop...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the robber...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just laughed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like he {\i1}wanted{\i0} the police to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was that cocky, he must have had a perfect escape plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or he thought he could survive jumping off a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that why he took his helmet off? Was it part of his plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think we need to find the identity of this robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, you can't come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he looks like someone I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that Atomura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I run a restaurant in the neighborhood. He's in all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he worked for Nekota{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s company...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nekota...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The truck the robber fell on was moving office equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for Nekota, that man over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Atomura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Atomura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he does work for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... Until last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:15:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's worked for me since I started my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we're in the middle of tough times, so I had to let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was part of our restructuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he was driven to do {\i1}this{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're trying to downsize your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The office space in this building is smaller and the rent is cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was your company before this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The top floor of that building there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right across the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we take a look at your old office?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he's been planning this robbery for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he may have left evidence in the old office space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you met these detectives before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never done anything wrong in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was his locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this was his desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've still got a lot of stuff here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted the new space to represent a fresh start,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I left the old furniture here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't see anything in his locker that might connect to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing in the desk either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you fired him a week ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how come all his belongings are still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to upset the other employees with the news that he'd been laid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to tell them he was on a business trip until we got the new office running.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told Atomura to come back after we moved and collect his things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the truck the robber fell on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the truck's down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:17:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We must be across from the building the robber jumped from!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the robber was trying to jump to this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gap is almost 9 meters across,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the robber was carrying a heavy bag full of jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless you were Kamen Yaiba,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you'd never try a stunt like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Kamen Yaiba would never steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, you can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, where were you when the movers were moving things out of this office?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, in my apartment downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You live under the balcony we were just on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The office was on the ninth floor, four floors above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a funny-looking helmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bicycle racing helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I used to do triathlons when I was young...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seen enough yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew Atomura for a long time, but you won't find anything connected to him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the police were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a robbery just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if this had anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name's Isaka. I live on the sixth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three days ago, around 2 AM, I woke up to a heavy thudding sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw a thin, stick-like shadow projected against the curtain by the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I woke my husband up and went out onto the balcony, but it was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:19:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband says I was dreaming, but I thought I should tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you live over this apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Room 605, right above this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that same sound at the time of the robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but I was watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything about the robbery until I heard the police sirens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we get back to work already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still need to make a bunch of round trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much stuff have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expanded my company too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It used to cover the entire ninth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something smells fishy here, but there's no reason not to rule is a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've taken pictures of the crime scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and we've got all the evidence, except that brooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found the fake gun and stolen jewels in the bag near the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see no reason to hold up the movers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:20:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please keep the plastic sheet on top of the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we'll need to confiscate the truck when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get this done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you started carrying stuff down to the truck,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where did you park?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the back door of this building,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the opposite side from the street with the new building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we drove around a back alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear anything at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The from that sewer construction they've been doing all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, what a racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Lots of noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:50.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A narrow back alley that not many people use...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of noise, that Nekota guy was a pain in the rear too, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! He insisted on giving us exact procedures for moving his stuff out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He made everyone, even the driver, come up to the office for a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once we got there, he kept us waiting forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he canceled twice, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Originally we were going to do the move two days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he called that morning and told us he'd had a sudden change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same thing happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was a perfect day to move! Nice and sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he did tell us beforehand that he might need to reschedule the move,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he paid us for all three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, it was good pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, I hope I never land a client like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! The rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mister! Good luck with the moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bedroom, bedroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:43.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:46.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:51.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If my deductions are correct, it's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:55.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes! It's wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:02.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it. This was no suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:09.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nekota murdered Atomura and covered up his crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:17.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}by jumping through time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.84,0:23:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you yelled at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know we're key witnesses to the jewelry store robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:16.12,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:21.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.37,0:24:23.84,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Give Sato-san the brooch and make a bold approach!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:24.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.92,0:24:25.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Huh?
